def get_change(M):
    coins = [1, 3, 4]
    min_num_coins = [0] * (M + 1)

    for m in range(1, M + 1):
        min_num_coins[m] = float('inf')
        for i in range(len(coins)):
            if m >= coins[i]:
                num_coins = min_num_coins[m - coins[i]] + 1
                if num_coins < min_num_coins[m]:
                    min_num_coins[m] = num_coins

    return min_num_coins[M]
